Morning, Uncle Wade.

01:00:34.698 --> 01:00:36.064
Papa went to town,

01:00:36.066 --> 01:00:39.167
said you needed
to set those traps.

01:00:43.107 --> 01:00:46.708
It's true
what you said...

01:00:46.710 --> 01:00:49.077
about Mom and all.

01:00:51.415 --> 01:00:54.950
Good man stands up
for his family...

01:00:56.086 --> 01:00:58.253
for his country.

01:00:58.255 --> 01:01:01.757
