to stay here

01:01:25.916 --> 01:01:27.282
and become
like my father.

01:01:27.284 --> 01:01:28.817
Hell, I wish the war
wasn't over,

01:01:28.819 --> 01:01:29.918
so that when
I was old enough,

01:01:29.920 --> 01:01:32.320
